data.description: Come and see this cute move-in ready 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home with 2 car garage! The kitchen is open to the living area and features skylights that let in lots of natural light. Plenty of room in your new backyard for a garden, plus a covered patio to keep cool in the summer heat and a fenced in dog run area + storage. Lots of infrastructure including shopping, dining & entertainment located within several miles.
